<item>
            <title>[FLINK-3504] Join fails while have expression inside join condition.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-3504</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;    val ds1 = CollectionDataSets.get3TupleDataSet(env).as(&apos;a, &apos;b, &apos;c)
    val ds2 = CollectionDataSets.get5TupleDataSet(env).as(&apos;d, &apos;e, &apos;f, &apos;g, &apos;h)
    val joinT = ds1.join(ds2).filter(&apos;a + 3 === &apos;d).select(&apos;c, &apos;g)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This query would throw exception:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;Caused by: org.apache.flink.api.table.TableException: Joins should have at least one equality condition
	at org.apache.flink.api.table.plan.rules.dataset.DataSetJoinRule.convert(DataSetJoinRule.scala:57)
	at org.apache.calcite.rel.convert.ConverterRule.onMatch(ConverterRule.java:116)
	at org.apache.calcite.plan.volcano.VolcanoRuleCall.onMatch(VolcanoRuleCall.java:228)
	... 44 more
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There are 2 issues here:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;DataSetJoinRule does not support expression inside join condition.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;JoinPushExpressionsRulewould add a Project to calculate expression value before Join, so the join condition does not include expression any more, however, it&apos;s not returned after the logical optimization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
</description>
